room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Symbology Escape Rooms in San Jose
review: We had a group of 6 people escape The Vault - it was amazing! I would say that the space is a bit tight with 6 people, but it still worked. The room is a challenge, but not impossible. This was our first time escaping a room, and this seemed like a great room to start with. We were able to get out, but with only 30 seconds to spare.Staff was friendly and helpful. The facility was well maintained, clean, and everything was in working order. Highly recommend!

room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Symbology Escape Rooms in San Jose
review: We went as a group of six to the Vault room. We had a lot of fun solving the puzzles. They had simple solutions and were yet tricky to solve. Overall, it was an amazing experience. I would definitely recommend it!

room_title: Escape room "The Vault" by Symbology Escape Rooms in San Jose
review: I love Paradox's games. I've played both and this one is an amazing and creative take on such a simple concept. Thank you for putting out such great games. Hope to see more from you in the future.
